      "content": "it's really creeping me out. i feel like i can't even relax in my own living room without being some kind of data point for them. if they're already using my home to train these models, what's next? do they have ways to use this to predict when someone might be \"unstable\" or something like that? i'm starting to feel like i should start covering my sensors or something.",
